<taxonomicName authorityName="González-Miguéns &amp; Soler-Zamora &amp; Villar-Depablo &amp; Todorov &amp; Lara" authorityYear="2022" box="[311,422,350,372]" class="Lobosa" family="Arcellidae" genus="Galeripora" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="22" pageNumber="1066" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="species" species="succelli">
<emphasis box="[311,422,350,372]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="1066">G. succelli</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and (2) the rough outlook of the test.
</paragraph>
